text: Bombie may refer to: ==Chiefs of Clan Maclellan== Any of a number of chiefs of Clan MacLellan: *Thomas Maclellan of Bombie *Patrick Maclellan of Bombie ==Other== * Bombie the Zombie, a fictional character in the Scrooge McDuck universe * Mother Bombie, the main character in the Elizabethan era stage play of the same name ==See also== * Bomby
title: Bombie
